ROS_INFO_STREAM("Result: " &lt;&lt; result);    // stream style
</code></pre> <p>Launchfile</p> <p>To see the output in the console set configuration to [screen]{.title-ref} in the launch file.</p> <pre><code>&lt;launch&gt;
